<br>
First, yes, Khaylee, Shaman are welcome on this daring adventure. All classes are welcome in fact. Bards make it easier to resist the dragons two AE attacks, Fear and Fire. <br>
<br>
It is recommended that you should try and get both of these resists up to around 80, without spells or songs. With other peoples buffs, resisting the dragons area effect attacks is easy. Remember, Holy cakes and Kaladim constutionals bother offer +5 to resists across the board, so there is +10 right there, without switching out other gear.<br>
<br>
I will be saying hello to everyone in game over the next few days, if you have any questions, I can try and answer them then.<br>
<br>
Thanks for the good wishes Mariuss. <br>
<br>
I feel very good about this raid on Lord Nagafen.<br>
<br>
Stavenham Valiant<br>
